Your dragon is very young, currently it will only be able to feed.
To feed it you will have to have food, when it gets older you will be able to play
with it which will make it grow faster and eventually you will be able to train
it to be a force to be reckoned with. 
In you pack you will be able to buy food to feed your dragon and toys for your
dragon to play with and equipment for your dragon to train it and it will grow 
even faster.